      <title>中国服务业扩张放缓 显现经济疲软新迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-services-expansion-cools-in-new-sign-of-economic-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项私人调查显示，中国服务业活动扩张低于预期，加剧了人们对经济健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
